												<event>
													<text>The Foolish laughs, and your heart warms at the rare sight. "Well, yes, we have hands." He pulls his hand back, before taking a deep breath and releasing it. Slowly, his body drifts back towards the floor, "Thhhhank you for cheering me up, captain... you're silly." He pauses, before getting flustered, "In a good way, thhhhough!" The Foolish hurries to float out of the room, and you get the feeling that he's blushing within his shell.</text>
