<event name="SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2" unique="true">
	<text>As you approach the Foolish's room, you notice strange, iridescent lights shimmering from within the cracks in his door... What in the Multiverse is going on in there?</text>
