				<event>
					<text>He sighs and begins to roll away, "Figured you'd be useless. Well, if you do see him, let him know thhhhat mattervirus of his transmogrified my toothhhbrush into a sentient globule of matter-devouring hatred again. Please remind him to refrain from using my toothhhbrush, before I turn his into a makeshift explosive." Alkali turns the corner, and you're only left wondering... do Shells really have teeth?</text>
