<event name="SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1" unique="true">
	<text>As you're looking for the Minister, the power to the ship briefly flickers off. A few moments later, it happens again, and you hear the man you're looking for cry out, "Why are you being greedy NOW? How much of this do you want, exactly?"</text>
